verbose_text: Particles of reconstituted BL100-(MBP) CEF, isolated (MBP) CEF, isolated ID2, and ID2 co-expressed with (MBP) CEF were imaged on a Tecnai G2 Spirit LaB6 transmission electron microscope (TEM; FEI) operating at 120 keV (Electron Microscopy Science Technology Platform, The Francis Crick Institute).
